  <div class="study-questions">
    <h2>Discussion Questions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        What does it mean to be "born again" ({{ scripture("John 3:3") }})? How is this different
        from physical birth?
      </li>
      <li>How does {{ scripture("John 3:16") }} summarize the entire gospel message?</li>
      <li>
        Why do people love darkness rather than light ({{ scripture("John 3:19") }})? What does this
        teach us about human nature?
      </li>
      <li>
        What can we learn from John the Baptist's attitude toward Christ's increasing popularity ({{
        scripture("John 3:30") }})?
      </li>
      <li>
        How should the truth that "whoever believes has eternal life" ({{ scripture("John 3:36") }})
        affect our evangelism?
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

